 javno,

1093
00:41:20,280 --> 00:41:22,120
 nema trenutka

1094
00:41:22,120 --> 00:41:22,980
 medijskog prostora

1095
00:41:22,980 --> 00:41:23,400
 koji sam dobio

1096
00:41:23,400 --> 00:41:24,440
 da to pitanje nisam postavio.

1097
00:41:24,440 --> 00:41:25,620
 Nikad nisam dobio odgovor.

1098
00:41:25,620 --> 00:41:26,180
 Kažu,

1099
00:41:26,180 --> 00:41:26,760
 hrvatski zakon,

1100
00:41:26,760 --> 00:41:27,480
 ja to ne možu.

1101
00:41:27,480 --> 00:41:28,360
 Ne možu,

1102
00:41:28,360 --> 00:41:29,040
