00:41:35,000 --> 00:41:35,780
 i te novce koristiti

1111
00:41:35,780 --> 00:41:36,640
 za političke potrebe.

1112
00:41:36,640 --> 00:41:37,220
 Ne može.

1113
00:41:37,220 --> 00:41:38,620
 A posebice ne može

1114
00:41:38,620 --> 00:41:39,680
 kad financiranje dolazi

1115
00:41:39,680 --> 00:41:41,880
 iz inozemnih instituta

1116
00:41:41,880 --> 00:41:44,260
 ili kako ih oni to vole nazivati,

1117
00:41:44,260 --> 00:41:45,980
 tek tad ne može.

1118
00:41:45,980 --> 00:41:46,900
 Međutim,

1119
00:41:46,900 --> 00:41:47,840
 nikad nikome nije,

1120
00:41:47,840 --> 00:41:49,180
 a nikad me niko nije ni tužio

1121
00:41:49,180 --> 00:41:50,280
 da ih levećem,

1122
00:41:50,280 --> 00:41:50,920
 da ih ne znam nešto,

1123
00:41:50,920 --> 00:41:52,100
 a ja ih optuživao za to.

1124
00:41:52,100 --> 00:41:52,780
 Zašto?

1125
00:41:53,620 --> 00:41:55,100
 Meni je to vrlo, vrlo simptomalno.

1126
00:41:55,100 --> 00:41:55,760
 Ali, evo, recimo,

1127
00:41:55,760 --> 00:41:56,800
 to je primjer

1128
00:41:56,800 --> 00:41:58,460
 kada vam je jedna takva udruga

1129
00:41:58,460 --> 00:42:00,420
 prevali 800-900 miliona kuna.

1130
00:42:00,420 --> 00:42:01,800
 Mi smo to javno iščitavali

1131
00:42:01,800 --> 00:42:02,580
 u tome trenutku

1132
00:42:02,580 --> 00:42:04,020
 preko svojih računa

1133
00:42:04,020 --> 00:42:05,060
 gdje imate projekte,

1134
00:42:05,060 --> 00:42:06,000
 ne znam tipa projekta

1135
00:42:06,000 --> 00:42:07,460
