1143
00:42:14,600 --> 00:42:15,560
 love otišlo

1144
00:42:15,560 --> 00:42:17,420
 na osobne dohodke,

1145
00:42:17,420 --> 00:42:18,600
 odnosno putovanja,

1146
00:42:18,900 --> 00:42:19,940
 osobno prezentacije.

1147
00:42:19,940 --> 00:42:20,760
 A znači,

1148
00:42:20,760 --> 00:42:21,700
