1149
00:42:21,700 --> 00:42:24,100
 Znači, ostalo je nekakvih 16 ili 15%

1150
00:42:24,100 --> 00:42:24,880
 od te love

1151
00:42:24,880 --> 00:42:26,080
 koji je usmjeren u projekat.

1152
00:42:26,080 --> 00:42:27,600
 Naravno, projekat se nikad nije ostvario

1153
00:42:27,600 --> 00:42:29,080
 jer nije bio realno ni ostvariv

1154
00:42:29,080 --> 00:42:30,520
 s obzirom na rashode

1155
00:42:30,520 --> 00:42:32,340
 koji su išli na osobne dohodke,

1156
00:42:32,340 --> 00:42:33,460
 odnosno osobne primitke.

1157
00:42:33,460 --> 00:42:35,060
 U potpuno se slažem s vama

1158
00:42:35,060 --> 00:42:36,640
 da te stvari treba ispitivati.

1159
00:42:36,640 --> 00:42:37,660
 Treba vidjeti zapravo

1160
00:42:37,660 --> 00:42:38,820
 taj novac koji je došao,

1161
00:42:38,820 --> 00:42:39,560
 kako je došao,

1162
00:42:39,560 --> 00:42:40,620
 za šta se koristio.

1163
00:42:40,620 --> 00:42:42,320
 Apsolutno se slažem tu sama.

1164
00:42:42,800 --> 00:42:44,700
 Nekako samo neki moj osobni dojam

1165
00:42:44,700 --> 00:42:46,540
 iz neke moje osobne vizure

1166
00:42:46,540 --> 00:42:47,860
 možemo prodebatirati o tome

1167
00:42:47,860 --> 00:42:49,520
 da većina zapravo

1168
00:42:49,520 --> 00:42:50,900
 u ekipe sa desne strane

1169
00:42:50,900 --> 00:42:52,440
 konzervativnih ljudi

1170
00:42:52,440 --> 00:42:53,840
 koji su u Hrvatskoj

1171
00:42:53,840 --> 00:42:55,760
 možda čak i više se fokusiraju

1172
00:42:55,760 --> 00:42:57,260
 na to otkud njima novac

1173
00:42:57,260 --> 00:42:58,800
 umjesto da ono što ste rekli

1174
00:42:58,800 --> 00:42:59,400
 na početku

1175
00:42:59,400 --> 00:43:00,740
 shvatimo da smo tu gdje jesmo,

1176
00:43:00,740 --> 00:43:01,940
 shvatimo da smo u toj igri,

1177
00:43:01,940 --> 00:43:03,940
 naučiš pravila te igre,

1178
00:43:03,940 --> 00:43:05,720
 ne kažem da sad na isti način

1179
00:43:05,720 --> 00:43:06,600
 prikupljaš novac,

1180
00:43:06,600 --> 00:43:08,720
 ali kao da Hrvatskoj desnici

1181
00:43:08,720 --> 00:43:11,040
 nedostaje konstruktivnosti,

1182
00:43:11,120 --> 00:43:15,280
 da naprave neku priču

1183
00:43:15,280 --> 00:43:16,320
 umjesto da pričaju samo

1184
00:43:16,320 --> 00:43:17,840
 kako su oni uspjeli novac.

1185
00:43:17,840 --> 00:43:18,700
 Jer nije ljevica kriva

1186
00:43:18,700 --> 00:43:20,080
 što su oni uspjeli zaraditi novac,

1187
00:43:20,080 --> 00:43:20,700
 desnica nije.

1188
00:43:20,700 --> 00:43:22,260
 Ja se s time nikako ne bi složio

1189
00:43:22,260 --> 00:43:23,600
 i možemo porazgovarati o tome.

1190
00:43:23,600 --> 00:43:25,300
 Ali recimo eklatantan primjer

1191
00:43:25,300 --> 00:43:26,440
 oga što govorim je recimo

1192
00:43:26,440 --> 00:43:28,080
 laudato televizije.

1193
00:43:28,080 --> 00:43:29,260
 Ako znate na što govorim.

1194
00:43:29,260 --> 00:43:31,000
 Dakle, to je priča koja

1195
00:43:31,000 --> 00:43:33,260
 nećemo isvrsati u političku sferu.

1196
00:43:33,260 --> 00:43:34,700
 Mislim da nema potrebe da to radimo.

1197
00:43:34,700 --> 00:43:36,320
 Ali sa neke njihove strane.

1198
00:43:36,320 --> 00:43:37,420
 Dakle, postoje mediji

1199
00:43:37,420 --> 00:43:39,140
 koje se ne slažu sa onime.

1200
00:43:39,140 --> 00:43:40,360
 Za što se oni zalažu?

1201
00:43:40,360 --> 00:43:42,440
 Oni su mogli tipkat po Facebooku

1202
00:43:42,440 --> 00:43:43,900
 koje ne funkcionira to tako.

1203
00:43:43,900 --> 00:43:45,000
 Njih financira ovaj,

1204
00:43:45,000 --> 00:43:45,780
 njih financira ovaj.

1205
00:43:45,780 --> 00:43:47,320
 Mogli su to napraviti.

1206
00:43:47,320 --> 00:43:49,040
 Ali nisu to napraviti.

1207
00:43:49,040 --> 00:43:50,220
 Nego je Ksenija Abramović

1208
00:43:50,220 --> 00:43:51,680
 i ostala ekipa koja je oko nje.

1209
00:43:51,680 --> 00:43:53,800
 Rekla, idemo pokrenuti neku priču.

1210
00:43:54,060 --> 00:43:55,120
 Idemo se formalizirati.

1211
00:43:55,120 --> 00:43:56,600
 Idemo napraviti nešto konstruktivno

