00:43:57,640 --> 00:43:59,500
 I napravili su fenomenalnu priču

1214
00:43:59,500 --> 00:44:00,600
 koja i dan danas traje

1215
00:44:00,600 --> 00:44:02,000
 i koja će trajati ako Bog

1216
00:44:02,000 --> 00:44:03,160
 da je još dugi niz godina.

1217
00:44:03,160 --> 00:44:05,840
 Moj komentar je da

1218
00:44:05,840 --> 00:44:06,760
 možda bi se

1219
00:44:06,760 --> 00:44:10,400
 radi zdravog načina razmišljanja

1220
00:44:10,400 --> 00:44:11,440
 u našem društvu

1221
00:44:11,440 --> 00:44:12,540
 trebala Hrvatska desnica

1222
00:44:12,540 --> 00:44:13,860
 možda i više fokusirati

1223
00:44:13,860 --> 00:44:15,180
 na te konkretne stvari

1224
00:44:15,180 --> 00:44:17,280
 kako se usprotiviti

1225
00:44:17,280 --> 00:44:18,700
 nekim stvarima koje mi smetaju.

1226
00:44:18,700 --> 00:44:20,080
 Znate zašto o sve govorim?

1227
00:44:20,080 --> 00:44:22,440
 Jer možemo prokomentirati to sve,

1228
00:44:22,560 --> 00:44:25,480
 ali bojim se da neke stvari

1229
00:44:25,480 --> 00:44:26,620
 neke ideje

1230
00:44:26,620 --> 00:44:27,940
 vi ste bili, vi ste puno duže

1231
00:44:27,940 --> 00:44:29,440
 nego ja, ali neke stvari

1232
00:44:29,440 --> 00:44:31,540
 koje se predlažu

1233
00:44:31,540 --> 00:44:32,400
 u hrvatskoj politici

1234
00:44:32,400 --> 00:44:33,360
 kao da dolaze samo

1235
00:44:33,360 --> 00:44:34,460
 iz te srčanosti.

1236
00:44:34,460 --> 00:44:37,120
 Ne dolaze iz nekih studija,

1237
00:44:37,120 --> 00:44:37,980
 iz nekog razuma

1238
00:44:37,980 --> 00:44:39,700
 što ja apsolutno razumijem.

1239
00:44:39,700 --> 00:44:41,800
 Ali ako želimo sudjelovati

1240
00:44:41,800 --> 00:44:42,160
 u ovo igri,

1241
